						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Backend REST API for a fictitious company managing clients, projects, and certifications. Role-based auth, CRUD endpoints, containerised with Docker.</p>
					<p class="tech">Node.js · Express · JWT · Docker</p>
				</div>

				<div class="project-card">
					<div class="project-title-row">
						<h3><a href="https://www.kaggle.com/code/itzi97/u-tad-dogs-vs-cats" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dogs vs Cats</a></h3>
						<div class="icons">
							<svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" title="TensorFlow"><path fill="#FF6F00" d="M1.292 5.856L11.54 0v24l-4.095-2.378V7.603l-6.168 3.564.015-5.31zm21.43 5.311l-6.168-3.564v13.605L12.46 24V0l10.247 5.856.015 5.31z"/></svg>
							<svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" title="Keras"><path fill="#D00000" d="M0 0v24h24V0zm12.923 5.465l2.17 2.17-2.17 2.17V5.465zM6.032 6.544l5.274 5.274-5.274 5.275V6.544zm5.97 5.97l.921.922-2.17 2.17-.921-.92zm1.839.002l3.127 3.126H12.84zm.005-1.843V7.547l3.124 3.125z"/></svg>
