						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Image classification using CNNs and transfer learning. Built and fine-tuned a Keras/TensorFlow model on the classic binary classification benchmark.</p>
					<p class="tech">Python · TensorFlow · Keras · Transfer Learning</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.eyebrow {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
		margin-top: 0;
	}
	.section-heading {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: end;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.section-heading h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}
	.section-heading p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 40rem;
	}
	.view-all {
		color: var(--accent);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}
	.view-all:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.project-title-row {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.6em;
		margin-bottom: 0.4em;
	}
	.project-title-row h3 {
		margin: 0;
	}
	.icons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.35em;
		align-items: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	.project-title-row .icons svg {
		width: 1.2em;
		height: 1.2em;
		font-size: 1em;
		vertical-align: middle;
		display: block;
	}
</style>
